name: Emsdata - Be Data Driven
body:
### How it works?

- Setup new project in our plaftorm. 
- Download data stream client SDK and start sending buisness events to our data lake. 
- View data catalogue and explore data you have collected. 
- Create cross buisness reports and be Data Driven.
